        <main class="policy-container">
            <section class="section-heading">
                <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
                <p>Effective Date: May 19, 2025</p>
            </section>

            <section class="policy-section">
                <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
                <p>FlyDreamAir is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your personal information when you use our services.</p>
            </section>

            <section class="policy-section">
                <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Name, email address, phone number, date of birth, payment details.</li>
                    <li><strong>Travel Data:</strong> Booking history, frequent flyer details, preferences.</li>
                    <li><strong>Technical Data:</strong> IP address, browser type, device information, cookies.</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="policy-section">
                <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>To process bookings and provide travel services.</li>
                    <li>To personalize your experience and deliver tailored offers.</li>
                    <li>To communicate updates, promotions, and important notices.</li>
                    <li>To comply with legal and regulatory obligations.</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="policy-section">
                <h2>4. Sharing of Information</h2>
                <p>We may share your data with trusted third parties, including payment processors, travel partners, and regulatory authorities, only when necessary for service delivery or compliance.</p>
            </section>

            <section class="policy-section">
                <h2>5. Data Security</h2>
                <p>Your data is protected using industry-standard encryption and access controls. While we strive to secure your information, no method is 100% secure.</p>
            </section>

            <section class="policy-section">
                <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Access or request a copy of your personal data.</li>
                    <li>Update or correct inaccurate information.</li>
                    <li>Request deletion or restrict processing of your data.</li>
                    <li>Withdraw consent for marketing communications at any time.</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="policy-section">
                <h2>7. Cookies</h2>
                <p>We use cookies to enhance site performance and personalize your experience. You can manage your cookie preferences through your browser settings.</p>
            </section>

            <section class="policy-section">
                <h2>8. Policy Updates</h2>
                <p>We may periodically update this policy. Changes will be posted on our website with the revised effective date.</p>
            </section>

            <section class="policy-section">
                <h2>9. Contact Us</h2>
                <p>If you have any questions or requests regarding this policy, contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@flydreamair.com">privacy@flydreamair.com</a>.</p>
            </section>
        </main>

